"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>label</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>min = 1</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>max = INT_MAX</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
